Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time to complete 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in comparison to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time it takes to move from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before moving to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' Cycle Time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' from case initiation
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time it takes 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' after the execution of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Minimum time between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case
